<object id="GUID-B73404C4-EAA5-4D5D-8609-6036A507D125" class="- topic/object "><desc class="- topic/desc "><p class="- topic/p ">Select required printer calibrations </p></desc><param name="testid" value="216002" class="- topic/param "/><param name="target" value="NIL" class="- topic/param "/><param name="axmodule" value="None" class="- topic/param "/></object> 
</p></section><section id="GUID-1156E15C-FA11-42F7-80CE-F9823F371FA9" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Function</title><p class="- topic/p ">Select which calibrations should be done in 
<xref keyref="SDS21-6-003" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-B828E436-A124-4809-981E-2DBE1E09A388.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 21-6-003 Execute selected printer calibrations [Special Tests]?>21-6-003 Execute selected printer calibrations [Special Tests]</xref>. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">In the addition tab Calibration Dates: it is possible to read the dates of the calibrations and the last successful execution. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-92369981-F020-4E62-9707-58F93D054214" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Description</title><p class="- topic/p ">This test can be run more than once to increase the number of calibrations executed. Each time the test is run you can select 1 calibration. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">It is possible to clear any calibrations previously selected and to start over again. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The calibrations must be executed by 
<xref keyref="SDS21-6-003" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-B828E436-A124-4809-981E-2DBE1E09A388.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 21-6-003 Execute selected printer calibrations [Special Tests]?>21-6-003 Execute selected printer calibrations [Special Tests]</xref>. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-CAB53886-53D4-4E0F-B6E4-F23235AF7530" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Procedure</title><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Start the test. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Select the desired calibration : 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">-- All calibrations needed (set all) --
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">-- No calibrations needed (clear all) -- 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Printhead nozzle optimization 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Carriage Y calibration. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Carriage array alignment. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Move engine adjustment. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Height adjust service. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Media transport calibration. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">M&amp;C scanner calibration. 
</p></li></ul></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Press Continue 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Repeat this test for additional calibrations. 
</p></li></ol></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-3AD12DA3-F651-4B11-BEB9-FD79AA9649BB.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>SDS</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
